data.description: This adorable 3-bedroom, 2-bath home is close to several amenities, including shopping, downtown, and a school. The home offers a split floor plan, ceiling fans, and two decks. Situated back from the street on a .41 acre lot, this home boasts a large yard with room for a plentiful garden. City water is available in the street. Newer roof, dishwasher and exterior paint. Room to park an RV along with enclosed storage space that could work as motorcycle parking. Large detached finished storage area behind the home with potential to become an office space, home gym, game room, etc. This home could be the investment that you have been waiting for!
